ğŸ”¹ Real-World Example

When a user opens a website:
	1.	Device sends request to router.
	2.	Router performs NAT and forwards traffic to ISP.
	3.	ISP routes traffic to the internet.
	4.	Response returns to router.
	5.	Router forwards data back to correct internal device.

